      "blocks": {
        "profile_6iypNX": {
          "type": "profile",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Group_56.png",
            "heading": "Coenzyme Q10 200 mg",
            "text": "<p>An essential cofactor for mitochondrial energy production, supporting heart health and cellular energy metabolism. Acts as a powerful antioxidant protecting cells from oxidative damage while supporting cardiovascular function. CoQ10 levels naturally decline with age, making supplementation important for maintaining energy levels, exercise performance, and long-term heart health.</p>",
            "color_text": "#ffffff",
            "color_background": "#171717"
          }
        },
        "profile_CJzzAD": {
          "type": "profile",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Group_63.png",
            "heading": "Lutein 10 mg",
            "text": "<p>A carotenoid antioxidant that selectively accumulates in the retina, providing protection against blue light damage and supporting long-term eye health. Helps maintain visual acuity, reduces eye strain from screen time, and may support cognitive function. As natural lutein leve</p>",
            "color_text": "#ffffff",
            "color_background": "#171717"
          }
        },
        "profile_tEtbhX": {
          "type": "profile",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Group_62.png",
            "heading": "Zeaxanthin 2 mg",
            "text": "<p>Works synergistically with lutein to form the macular pigment, providing enhanced protection for the central retina and supporting sharp, clear vision. Helps filter harmful blue light, reduces glare sensitivity, and supports overall eye comfort during daily activities. Essential for maintaining long-term eye health and visual performance as you age.</p>",
            "color_text": "#ffffff",
            "color_background": "#171717"
          }
        },
        "profile_wjL8UK": {
          "type": "profile",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Group_63.png",
            "heading": "Astaxanthin 6 mg",
            "text": "<p>One of nature's most potent antioxidants, providing comprehensive cellular protection and supporting skin health, eye health, and exercise recovery. Helps reduce inflammation, supports cardiovascular health, and may improve skin elasticity and hydration. Research shows it can help reduce exercise-induced fatigue and support overall vitality and healthy aging.</p>",
            "color_text": "#ffffff",
            "color_background": "#171717"
          }
        }
      },
