          "type": "profile",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Group_57.png",
            "heading": "Glucosamine Sulphate 750 mg",
            "text": "<p>Supports joint health and cartilage repair during overnight recovery when your body naturally rebuilds and repairs tissues. Helps maintain joint flexibility, reduces morning stiffness, and supports the body's natural healing processes. Taking it in the evening aligns with your body's natural repair cycle for optimal joint support and long-term mobility.</p>",
