            "text": "<p>A trace mineral that supports brain health, mood stability, and cognitive function at safe nutritional doses. May help protect neurons, support healthy brain aging, and promote emotional balance. Research suggests it can support longevity pathways and help maintain cognitive clarity and mental resilience as you age, making it an important component of brain health optimization.</p>",
